    "body": "Well the experience I have right now is pretty similar to the sandbox you sent.\r\n\r\nIn the example you sent there are brands. Right now they are a taxonomy of each product.\r\nSo in your example, if you would like to display the logo next to each brand in the refinementlist, how would this be done?\r\n\r\nI have indexed another indices containing all the brands. This contains logo, description, etc about each brand. I want to display this information in the refinementlist for my main indices (instant_search in your example).\r\n\r\nI've dont know where to start on this functionality so I dont have any code to show you for it, all i've done is index all brands separately.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
